Installation
--------------

.. start installation

``snippet-fmt`` can be installed from PyPI.

To install with ``pip``:

.. code-block:: bash

	$ python -m pip install snippet-fmt

.. end installation


.. code-block:: python

	def foo(bar):
		print("hello")


.. code-block:: TOML

	hello = "world
